---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Charter">
  <section class="container" style="padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md); max-width: 720px;">
    <h1>Charter</h1>
    <p style="color: var(--ink-muted); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
      Ground Zero · Rev 1.3 · full document lives in the project repo.
    </p>
    <p>
      👉 <a href="https://github.com/sowthri-industrial-ai/project-00-ground-zero/blob/main/docs/00-charter.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read the full Charter on GitHub</a>
    </p>

    <h2>Operating principles</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Platform before payload</li>
      <li>Portfolio-grade · not production-grade</li>
      <li>Full public source · nothing private</li>
      <li>Ephemeral Azure endpoints (ADR-0013)</li>
      <li>Governance before code</li>
      <li>Deliberate failure branches (ADR-0011)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Definition of Done · 13 criteria</h2>
    <p>All 13 Ground Zero DoD criteria listed in the Charter § 14.</p>

    <h2>ADRs · 20 decisions recorded</h2>
    <p>All architectural decisions live in <code>docs/03-ADR/</code> · MADR format.</p>
  </section>
</Base>
